    "The objectives of adaptation should be not only holding interest, but also fostering deeper understanding.",
    "Resource Scheduling SystemsReinforcement learning has been applied to optimize resource scheduling in educational institutions, such as classroom assignments, teacher workloads, and laboratory use.",
